                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Thrill came slowly<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 like a Boon for </l>
                    <l>Centuries delayed </l>
                    <l>It's fitness growing<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 like the Flood </l>
                    <l>In sumptuous<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 solitude - </l>
                    <l>The desolation only<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 missed</l>
                    <l>While Rapture<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 changed it's Dress </l>
                    <l>And stood arrayed<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 before the<add type="alternate" extent="change">Boon &amp;#x2022; news</add>
 change </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="">[And stood] before the suddenness / In simple Holiness -</add>
In<add type="alternate" extent="ravished Holiness">dazzling Holiness</add>
 ravished<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Holiness - </l>
                </lg>

